<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>

    <!--link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.0.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" /-->
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/index.css' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="drop-shadow"></div>

    <div id="modal-intro" class="modal center">
      Most people over the age of 10 dream at least 4 to 6 times per night
      during a stage of sleep. However, people suffering of brain tumors are
      unable to dream anymore.
      <br /><br />
      We have created a playground that allows each of us to customize immersive
      dreams in virtual reality.
      <br /><br />
      <strong><em>Feel free to explore your own DreamNA.</em></strong>
    </div>

    <div id="modal-question-1" class="modal center horizontal-center-buttons">
      How would you envisage the world?
      <br /><br />
      <button value="e_saturation:-100">Black and White</button>
      <button>Color</button>
    </div>

    <div id="modal-question-2" class="modal center horizontal-center-buttons">
      How do you feel?
      <br /><br />
      <button value="e_gamma:-100">Anxious</button>
      <button value="e_gamma:-50">Happy</button>
      <button value="e_gamma:50">Sad</button>
      <button value="e_gamma:100">Angry</button>
    </div>

    <div id="modal-question-3" class="modal center horizontal-center-buttons">
      If you were to direct your own dreams, what genre would you choose?
      <br /><br />
      <button>Very realistic</button>
      <button>Somewhat realistic</button>
      <button>Somewhat Fantastic</button>
      <button>Fantastic</button>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jquery@3.3.1/dist/jquery.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

    <script src="/js/index.js" type="application/javascript"></script>
  </body>
</html>
